<!-- rnb-source-begin eyJkYXRhIjoiYGBgclxuYGBgclxuZWJpcmRfdGF4JHNwZWNpZXNfbmFtZSA9IHdvcmQoZWJpcmRfdGF4JGViaXJkX3NwZWNpZXNfZnVsbG5hbWUsIDEsIDIsIHNlcCA9ICcgJylcbmhlYWQoZWJpcmRfdGF4KVxuYGBgXG5gYGAifQ== -->

## Build initial taxonomy mapping with straight forward species

<!-- rnb-text-end -->


<!-- rnb-chunk-begin -->


<!-- rnb-source-begin eyJkYXRhIjoiYGBgclxuYGBgclxuZWJpcmRfYmlyZGxpZmVfdGF4b25vbXlfbWFwcGluZyA9IGlubmVyX2pvaW4oXG4gIGJpcmRsaWZlX3RheFssIGMoJ3NwZWNpZXNfbmFtZScsICdiaXJkbGlmZV9pZCcsICdiaXJkbGlmZV9jb21tb25fbmFtZScpXSwgXG4gIGViaXJkX3RheFssIGMoJ3NwZWNpZXNfbmFtZScsICdlYmlyZF9pZCcsICdlYmlyZF9jb21tb25fbmFtZScsICdlYmlyZF9zcGVjaWVzX2Z1bGxuYW1lJyldXG4pXG5gYGBcbmBgYCJ9 -->

```r
```r
ebird_birdlife_taxonomy_mapping = inner_join(
  birdlife_tax[, c('species_name', 'birdlife_id', 'birdlife_common_name')], 
  ebird_tax[, c('species_name', 'ebird_id', 'ebird_common_name', 'ebird_species_fullname')]
)

<!-- rnb-source-end -->

<!-- rnb-output-begin eyJkYXRhIjoiSm9pbmluZywgYnkgPSBcXHNwZWNpZXNfbmFtZVxcXG4ifQ== -->

Joining, by = _name




<!-- rnb-output-end -->

<!-- rnb-source-begin eyJkYXRhIjoiYGBgclxuYGBgclxuZWJpcmRfYmlyZGxpZmVfdGF4b25vbXlfbWFwcGluZyRlYmlyZF9zcGVjaWVzX25hbWUgPSBlYmlyZF9iaXJkbGlmZV90YXhvbm9teV9tYXBwaW5nJHNwZWNpZXNfbmFtZVxuaGVhZChlYmlyZF9iaXJkbGlmZV90YXhvbm9teV9tYXBwaW5nKVxuYGBgXG5gYGAifQ== -->

```r
```r

```r
mapped_by_alternative_name = inner_join(
  birdlife_species_missing_from_ebird_with_alt_name[, c('species_name', 'birdlife_id', 'birdlife_common_name', 'alternative_name')], 
  ebird_tax[, c('species_name', 'ebird_id', 'ebird_common_name', 'ebird_species_fullname')],
  by = c('alternative_name' = 'species_name')
)
names(mapped_by_alternative_name) = c('species_name', 'birdlife_id', 'birdlife_common_name', 'ebird_species_name', 'ebird_id', 'ebird_common_name', 'ebird_species_fullname')
mapped_by_alternative_name = mapped_by_alternative_name[,c('species_name', 'birdlife_id', 'birdlife_common_name', 'ebird_id', 'ebird_common_name', 'ebird_species_fullname', 'ebird_species_name')]

<!-- rnb-source-begin eyJkYXRhIjoiYGBgclxuYGBgclxuYmlyZGxpZmVfc3BpbG9wZWxpYV9zdXJhdGVuc2lzID0gY2JpbmQoXG4gIGViaXJkX3RheFtlYmlyZF90YXgkc3BlY2llc19uYW1lID09ICdTcGlsb3BlbGlhIGNoaW5lbnNpcycsIGMoJ2ViaXJkX2lkJywgJ2ViaXJkX3NwZWNpZXNfbmFtZScsICdlYmlyZF9zcGVjaWVzX2Z1bGxuYW1lJywgJ2ViaXJkX2NvbW1vbl9uYW1lJyldLFxuICBiaXJkbGlmZV90YXhbYmlyZGxpZmVfdGF4JHNwZWNpZXNfbmFtZSA9PSAnU3BpbG9wZWxpYSBzdXJhdGVuc2lzJywgYygnYmlyZGxpZmVfaWQnLCAnc3BlY2llc19uYW1lJywgJ2JpcmRsaWZlX2NvbW1vbl9uYW1lJyldXG4pXG5lYmlyZF9iaXJkbGlmZV90YXhvbm9teV9tYXBwaW5nID0gcmJpbmQoZWJpcmRfYmlyZGxpZmVfdGF4b25vbXlfbWFwcGluZywgYmlyZGxpZmVfc3BpbG9wZWxpYV9zdXJhdGVuc2lzKVxuYmlyZGxpZmVfc3BpbG9wZWxpYV9zdXJhdGVuc2lzXG5gYGBcbmBgYCJ9 -->

```r
```r
birdlife_spilopelia_suratensis = cbind(
  ebird_tax[ebird_tax$species_name == 'Spilopelia chinensis', c('ebird_id', 'ebird_species_name', 'ebird_species_fullname', 'ebird_common_name')],
  birdlife_tax[birdlife_tax$species_name == 'Spilopelia suratensis', c('birdlife_id', 'species_name', 'birdlife_common_name')]
)
ebird_birdlife_taxonomy_mapping = rbind(ebird_birdlife_taxonomy_mapping, birdlife_spilopelia_suratensis)
birdlife_spilopelia_suratensis

# Map to Jetz
Load my mapping from Birdlife V8 to Jetz, this maps down the birdlife taxonomy versions to Birdlife V3 and thus Jetz. This version contains no extinct species.

## Prune Phylogeny and store

<!-- rnb-text-end -->


<!-- rnb-chunk-begin -->


<!-- rnb-source-begin eyJkYXRhIjoiYGBgclxuYGBgclxuc2VsZWN0ZWRfc3BlY2llcyA8LSBlYmlyZF9iaXJkbGlmZV9qZXR6X3RheG9ub215X21hcHBpbmckamV0el9zcGVjaWVzX25hbWVcbnBydW5lZF90cmVlIDwtIGxhZGRlcml6ZShkcm9wLnRpcChqZXR6X3BoeWxvX3RyZWUsIHNldGRpZmYoamV0el9waHlsb190cmVlJHRpcC5sYWJlbCwgc2VsZWN0ZWRfc3BlY2llcykpKVxud3JpdGUudHJlZShwcnVuZWRfdHJlZSwgZmlsZW5hbWUoVEFYT05PTVlfT1VUUFVUX0RJUiwgJ3BoeWxvZ2VueS50cmUnKSlcbmBgYFxuYGBgIn0= -->

```r
```r
selected_species <- ebird_birdlife_jetz_taxonomy_mapping$jetz_species_name
pruned_tree <- ladderize(drop.tip(jetz_phylo_tree, setdiff(jetz_phylo_tree$tip.label, selected_species)))
write.tree(pruned_tree, filename(TAXONOMY_OUTPUT_DIR, 'phylogeny.tre'))
